Portions derived from the original project, as required by the Apache License 2.0:

  - Runner animation frames (PNG artwork) under src/Resources/Runners/ are copied
    unmodified from the original project.
  - The runner frame-order patterns, the CPU→animation-speed formula, and the
    Custom Metrics JSON schema are reimplemented from the original.

Significant changes made in this port:

  - Complete rewrite from Swift / SwiftUI (macOS) to C# / .NET WinForms (Windows).
  - System-tray integration, animation loop, and CPU sampling reimplemented on
    Windows APIs (GetSystemTimes, Shell_NotifyIcon, DWM system backdrop).
  - Metrics dashboard reimplemented as a native Windows 11 tray flyout.
  - The macOS-only dashboard settings window, metrics bar, runner gallery,
    localization, and donation UI are not ported.
